description	"Jedi Demolitionist:
A very specialized Jedi, trained to use explosives in addition to a single lightsaber, medium combat style, the demolitionist has only a few low-level powers.

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber
-- Medium Style Only
-- Saber Defense (2)
-- EX Saber Throw (1) ^3[CS1]
-- 20% Less DMG
- 20 Det Packs

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Push (1)
- Pull (1)
- Sense (1)
- Absorb (1)

^8Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps
- Mind Trick Immunity (1)
- Bunny Hop (1)
- Slow Faller
- Cortosis (1)
- Force Block / Focus (3)
- 1 Extra Life"